item.title: About Me
item.author: mjs2600@gmail.com (Michael Simpson)
item.description: I live in Middlebury, Vermont with my wife, Mary Jane, and two small children. I am the chief data scientist at Snthesis and a graduate from Georgia Tech’s OMSCS program. I also love to hike and play the ukulele.
